datasets.name: ee4342c9
queryLines:
select *, regexp_extract(response.error_message, r":(.*?):", 1) errors, response.status_code status_code,
request_params.share_name, request_params.recipient_name, request_params.recipient_authentication_type share_type, request_params.is_ip_access_denied  from system.access.audit where event_date >= date_sub(current_date(), 7) and service_name = "unityCatalog" and action_name in ('deltaSharingListShares', 'deltaSharingGetShare','deltaSharingListSchemas', 'deltaSharingListAllTables', 'deltaSharingListTables',
'deltaSharingGetTableMetadata', 'deltaSharingGetTableVersion', 'deltaSharingQueryTable', 'deltaSharingQueryTableChanges', 'deltaSharingQueriedTable',
'deltaSharingQueriedTableChanges', 'deltaSharingListNotebookFiles', 'deltaSharingQueryNotebookFile', 'deltaSharingListFunctions', 'deltaSharingListAllFunctions',
'deltaSharingListFunctionVersions', 'deltaSharingListVolumes', 'deltaSharingListAllVolumes') and event_date >= date_sub(current_date(),700)

datasets.name: c13e7f0f
queryLines:
SELECT re.*, ip.allowed_ip_range, case when re.recipient_name not in (select distinct recipient_name FROM `system`.information_schema.share_recipient_privileges) then "share not assigned" else "share assigned" end share_status
, retrieval_status, token_status FROM (select * from system.information_schema.recipients where recipient_owner != 'System user') re LEFT JOIN  
(select recipient_name, collect_list(allowed_ip_range) allowed_ip_range  from system.information_schema.recipient_allowed_ip_ranges group by recipient_name)  ip
on re.recipient_name = ip.recipient_name LEFT JOIN (SELECT *,
case when activation_url is null then 'retrieved' else 'not retrieved' end as retrieval_status,
case when expiration_time > current_timestamp() and expiration_time <= date_add(current_timestamp(), 7) then 'expiring soon' else case when expiration_time < current_timestamp() then 'expired' else case when expiration_time > "9999-12-31" then "never expire" else 'not expiring soon' end end end as token_status FROM 
(SELECT *
FROM (
    SELECT *,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY recipient_name ORDER BY created DESC) as row_num
    FROM system.information_schema.recipient_tokens
)
WHERE row_num = 1)) to ON re.recipient_name = to.recipient_name
